If you're not gonna eat,
doc says sleep.

33
00:02:45,627 --> 00:02:47,595
Get your strength back.

34
00:02:47,629 --> 00:02:48,830
Mm.

35
00:02:48,864 --> 00:02:53,467
So, you stay lyin' down,
you,

36
