...his back still straight,

60
00:04:20,952 --> 00:04:22,553
Molly: [ Laughs ]
Blow.

61
00:04:22,588 --> 00:04:24,422
...visited by his children

62
00:04:24,456 --> 00:04:26,891
- and grandchildren...
- There you go!

63
00:04:26,925 --> 00:04:28,926
...people of accomplishment...

64
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:31,095
Man: Yay!

65
