and enlightenment.

71
00:04:45,476 --> 00:04:47,511
[ Grunts ]

72
00:04:47,545 --> 00:04:49,446
- And I worried...
- [ Laughs ]

73
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:51,347
...that the future I'd seen...

74
00:04:51,382 --> 00:04:52,616
[ Gunshot ]

75
00:04:52,650 --> 00:04:54,951
...magical
and filled with light...

76
00:04:54,985 --> 00:04:58,187
[ Laughter ]

77
00:04:58,222 --> 00:05:00,123
[ Laughs ]
Yeah.

78
00:05:00,157 --> 00:05:02,392
...might never come to pass.

79
00:05:05,062 --> 00:05:06,830
- [ Siren wailing ]
- [ Sighs ]

80
00:05:06,864 --> 00:05:07,997
Hank: Go.

81
