Gale...

217
00:14:29,295 --> 00:14:31,930
be reasonable.

218
00:14:51,116 --> 00:14:52,617
[ Slurps ]

219
00:14:57,990 --> 00:15:00,324
From this moment
forward,

220
00:15:00,359 --> 00:15:06,598
I decree no more schnitzel
or strudel.

221
00:15:06,632 --> 00:15:10,134
Let's get some American food
up in this.

222
00:15:14,171 --> 00:15:15,338
[ Whistles ]

223
00:15:22,279 --> 00:15:23,780
[ Engine shuts off ]

224
00:15:58,516 --> 00:16:00,150
[ Door closes ]

225
00:16:00,184 --> 00:16:02,185
[ Clock ticking ]

226
00:16:08,025 --> 00:16:10,860
[ Exhales slowly ]

227
